  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the salt, black pepper, ground cumin seeds, ground coriander seeds, garam masala, turmeric powder, and ground cayenne pepper.",
    "Sprinkle mixture over lamb leg and rub evenly into meat. Let sit at room temperature for 15 minutes.",
    "Place lamb on a wire rack in a shallow baking dish. Bake until internal temperature reaches 135°F (60°C), about 45-60 minutes, flipping halfway through cooking time.",
    "Let rest before slicing and serving."
